ER24&#8217;s Russel Meiring says at least one passenger has been critically injured. JOHANNESBURG - Ten people have been injured in a crash involving four cars outside Stellenbosch. Officials on scene found one car on its side along the R44, while two others collided in the middle of the road.ER24 s Russel Meiring says at least one passenger has been critically injured. We immediately began treating the patients and provided the seriously and critically injured with advanced life support interventions. Once treated, the patients were transported to the nearest hospitals for further treatment. One of the critically injured was airlifted by the helicopter to hospital. (Edited by Winnie Theletsane)